         MACRO   -- REGISTER --    REGISTER EQUATES
         REGISTER &LINK=R9,&PREFIX=SFI
.*
.*       REGISTER WILL GENERATE THE REGISTER DEFINITIONS R0
.*       THROUGH R15. IN ADDITION, A REGISTER EQUATE WILL BE
.*       GENERATED FOR A LABEL CALLED LINK. A GLOBAL SETC
.*       SYMBOL WILL ALSO BE DEFINED AND INITIALIZED BY THIS
.*       MACRO, &PFX THE PREFIX TO BE ASSOCIATED WITH THIS
.*       ROUTINE. OPERANDS FOR THIS MACRO ARE:
.*
.*       LINK=     DEFINES THE REGISTER TO BE ASSOCIATED WITH
.*                 LABEL LINK. THE DEFAULT IS R9.
.*
.*       PREFIX=   DEFINES THE PREFIX TO BE SAVED IN THE &PFX
.*                 GLOBAL SETC. DEFAULT IS SFI.
.*
.*
         GBLC  &PFX
         LCLA  &T
*
*              REGISTER DEFINITIONS
*
.LOOP    ANOP
R&T      EQU   &T
&T       SETA  &T+1
         AIF   (&T LE 15).LOOP
         SPACE 1
LINK     EQU   &LINK
&PFX     SETC  '&PREFIX'
         SPACE 2
         MEND
